    <label>steel golem</label>
    <description>Steel deposits exhibiting temporary animation when approached or damaged. How refined metal retains psychoreactive properties after processing is poorly understood - it suggests the alterations run deeper than surface contamination. The construct defends aggressively until the disturbance fades, then reverts to inert metal. Whether this was intentional design or unintended consequence remains a mystery.</description>
    <statBases>
      <MoveSpeed>3.9</MoveSpeed>
      <ArmorRating_Blunt>0.45</ArmorRating_Blunt>
      <ArmorRating_Sharp>0.9</ArmorRating_Sharp>
      <PsychicSensitivity>0.75</PsychicSensitivity>
    </statBases>
