  <!-- Silver Golem -->
  <ThingDef ParentName="MOL_BaseGolem">
    <defName>MOL_Golem_Silver</defName>
    <label>silver golem</label>
    <description>Silver formations that can spontaneously animate when disturbed. Psychoreactive alterations from ancient archotech presence allow the precious metal to move and attack threats, though no one knows why silver specifically exhibits such strong responses. The animation is temporary - the same deposit might remain dormant for years, animate briefly when drilled, then return to ordinary rock. The mechanism defies conventional understanding.</description>
